Dana Air has hailed the recently launched campaign against fake news by the Federal Government. The Minister of Information and Culture, Lai Mohammed, had launched the campaign nationwide and in the Diaspora, advising Nigerians to be wary of fake news. Dana Air Media and Communication Officer Kingsley Ezenwa, while receiving the award of the most socially responsible airline conferred on the airline at the 22nd summit of League of Airport and Aviation Correspondents yesterday, said the campaign was timely and in the right direction.